Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.48,0:31:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你看着他回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He'll be back, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.63,0:31:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.39,0:31:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\b1}人的善恶就这样来了又去，时间如流水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"And so the good and evil of men comes and goes, and time is like a flowing river."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.28,0:31:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\b1}剧终\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}THE END
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.96,0:32:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟瘾太大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They smoke like chimneys.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.64,0:32:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您应该付票钱 不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go and buy a ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.21,0:32:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}不
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.87,0:32:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣母啊  怎么了  我不给你们点教训  就不配叫我的名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll make mincemeat out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.90,0:32:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}一群混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.60,0:33:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-安娜女士  -从这进  出...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Signora Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.38,0:33:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}艾佛特
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.16,0:33:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不进来  你的妻子让我给你带吃的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't blame me, your wife told me to bring your lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.08,0:33:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我  我给妈妈说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Give it to me. - I told Mum
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.00,0:33:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不再给我胶片  不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you didn't give me the film. It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.84,0:33:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为胶片会着火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I thought you were joking when you said
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.93,0:33:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the film could catch fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.51,0:33:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想对你说这个  我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I just wanted to tell you. Now I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.02,0:33:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多  过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Toto … come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.23,0:33:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,往前  来这  坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.86,0:33:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细听我对你说  我做这个工作10年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, listen. I started this job when I was ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.74,0:34:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时没有这种现代的机器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We didn't have these modern machines then.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.37,0:34:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,影片是无声的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Films were silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.83,0:34:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放映机像这样  用手转动手柄操作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You turned the projector by hand with a crank.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.05,0:34:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天都用手柄操作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All day long!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.55,0:34:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样通过手柄\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And it was hard, this damned crank.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.01,0:34:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果累了  就失去速度了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you got tired, and slowed down a bit …
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.97,0:34:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一下子...  呜  所有都着火了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}everything was burned, in a flash.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.06,0:34:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不教我  现在不用手柄不是更方便了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So why don't you teach me, now there's no crank and it's easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.36,0:34:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我不愿意  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Because I don't want to, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.74,0:34:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不应该做这个工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This is no job for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.45,0:34:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像个奴隶  总是一个人待着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You work like a slave, always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.79,0:34:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一部影片看上百遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You watch the same film 100 times. Nothing else to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.42,0:34:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像个疯子一样和葛丽泰·嘉宝  泰隆·鲍华说话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You end up talking to Greta Garbo and Tyrone Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.63,0:34:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像头驴子一样工作  甚至所有的节日  复活节  圣诞节都错过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Always working. Every holiday, Easter, Christmas …
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.97,0:35:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有星期五才休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You only get Good Friday off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.30,0:35:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  如果耶稣不被钉在十字架上  连周五都要工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And if they hadn't put Christ on a cross, we'd work even then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.39,0:35:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么不换工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So why don't you change jobs?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.70,0:35:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是个笨蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Because I'm stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.53,0:35:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇上还有几个人能懂得操作  除了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who else around here would be a projectionist? No one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.46,0:35:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有像我一样一小部分人可以做这个工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It takes an imbecile like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.25,0:35:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而我运气不佳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.71,0:35:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我小的时候有战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I was little, there was the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.22,0:35:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我长大的时候又有另一场战争\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I grew up, there was another war.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.22,0:35:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你想当个像我一样的小傻瓜吗  -回答我  -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So, you want to be a stick-in-the-mud like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.98,0:35:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说得好  多多  说得好  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.82,0:35:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是为你好才说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.57,0:35:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里关上后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Always stuck in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.03,0:36:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天热死  冬天冷死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Boiling hot in summer, freezing cold in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.28,0:36:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼吸烟和汽油味  最后挣得少的可怜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Breathing in fumes, and earning a pittance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.95,0:36:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一点都不喜欢你做的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is it all bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.21,0:36:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着时间习惯了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You get used to it. And then, from up here
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.88,0:36:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当在上面听到电影院人满了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when the cinema is full,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.84,0:36:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家愉快地笑  你也感到高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you hear people laughing, and that makes you happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.97,0:36:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别人笑的时候你也开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It makes you feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.97,0:36:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像你让他们笑一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Like you're the one who makes them laugh
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.35,0:36:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们让你忘记不幸和悲伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and makes them forget their troubles.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点我喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That, I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.87,0:36:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说什么来着  还是白说  你看什么  你看什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You didn't hear a word I said. What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.08,0:36:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我一个你刚刚耍我的理由\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can't turn my back for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.04,0:36:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你母亲说的对  你是个疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your mother is right. You're mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.92,0:37:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么做到的  通过观察学到了不少另一个世界的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How on earth did he do it? He watches and learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.53,0:37:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}多多
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.72,0:37:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要告诉收纳员  你再也不能进电影院\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll tell the manager not to let you in. Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.35,0:37:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还要告诉阿德尔福神父\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I'll tell Father Adelfio.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.27,0:37:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缺少一个小神职人员  不能再倒霉了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No more altar boy, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.52,0:37:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佛特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Alfredo!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.27,0:37:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-去你妈的  -中了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Get stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.24,0:37:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊  我中了12  我的天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've won! I've won the pools!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.82,0:37:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}那个拿波里人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.46,0:37:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿波里人赢得了西沙[一种意大利乐透]\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Ciccio from Naples has won the pools!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.43,0:37:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸运的小子  那个拿波里人中了12  大家快跑啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Neapolitan has won the pools! Come along, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.27,0:37:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北方人都幸运\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}These Northerners have all the luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.26,0:38:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,广场是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The square is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.14,0:38:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下  停下  怎么了  你有马虱吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Keep still! Are the horse-flies bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.15,0:38:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有一堆的虱子  走吧  走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've a louse factory up here. Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.50,0:39:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要给你们一拳  你们想要干嘛  回家  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What do you want? Off you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.89,0:39:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个商人有两个店铺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A shopkeeper owns two shops.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.27,0:39:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个卖水果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In one, he sells fruit …
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.02,0:39:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Be seated.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.03,0:39:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教授  有外部的考生参加小学毕业考试  进来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Here are the external candidates for the School Certificate.
