Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.06,1:23:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  你说什么  我是艾琳娜的母亲  你个蠢货\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Who's that? - Elena's mother, you cretin.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.77,1:23:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  女士  我没有想到  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm sorry, madam. I really didn't know …
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.49,1:23:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bloody hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.99,1:23:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早告诉过你了  你觉得我是胡说八道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I told you. You thought I was kidding you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.45,1:23:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那些蓝眼睛的姑娘的确是最难追的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Take it from me. The blue-eyed ones are the worst.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.38,1:23:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不要再想这件事了  多多  感情这件事是无法明白的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Forget it, Toto. Feelings can never be understood.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.30,1:23:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也做不了什么让她明白  只能靠你的花言巧语  大概就是你之前做的那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- You can't explain them. - Oh, you made the world!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.47,1:23:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多  冷静  别置气  我只说说而已\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, don't get angry with me. What's come over you?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.98,1:23:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多  来这里  多多  你在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Out of the way. You mad? - Toto, come here!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.78,1:24:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没法自己走路啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Can't see where I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.46,1:24:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又这样  你得好好注意你的言行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How dare you talk to me like that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.92,1:24:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是赞美天主\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}With all due respect to the Lord,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.80,1:24:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他用来两三天就创造了世界\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}who made the world in three days.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.51,1:24:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我浪费了一些时间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd have taken longer,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.01,1:24:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有些事情  不谦虚的说  变得更好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}but certain things I could have done better.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.18,1:24:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你发现我怎么说的了么  你总是要回应所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Like I said, you have all the answers.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.44,1:24:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你快乐  多多  现在我给你讲一个故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll tell you a story. Just for you, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.07,1:24:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们坐一会  哎哟  太难了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let's sit down. God Almighty!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.91,1:24:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Once upon a time …
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.04,1:24:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个国王进行宴会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}a king gave a feast.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.54,1:24:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王国里最美的公主们都来参加了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The most beautiful princesses were there.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.28,1:24:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}够了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.84,1:24:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个守卫的士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A soldier who was standing guard
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.51,1:25:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见了国王的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}saw the king's daughter go by.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.22,1:25:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是最美的  他立刻爱上了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She was the loveliest one, and he fell instantly in love.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.97,1:25:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他只是一个贫穷的士兵  怎么比得上国王的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But what is a simple soldier next to the daughter of a king?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.11,1:25:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉了她没有她自己活不下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and told her he could no longer live without her.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.86,1:25:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主对他强烈的感情十分感动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The princess was so taken by the depth of his feeling
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.62,1:25:29.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就告诉士兵说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}that she said to the soldier,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.25,1:25:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有耐心...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"If you can wait for 100 days
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.25,1:25:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的阳台下等100个白天和夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"and 100 nights under my balcony
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.42,1:25:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就是你的了  作死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"I shall be yours."
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.38,1:25:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵立刻照做  等了1天  2天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}With that, the soldier went and waited one day, two days
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.76,1:25:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10天  20天...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}then ten, twenty.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.02,1:25:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天晚上公主都从窗户了查岗  士兵从不动摇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Each evening the princess looked out, and he never moved!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.44,1:26:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风雨还是大雪  一直在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Always there, come rain, come thunder.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.40,1:26:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕鸟拉屎  哪怕蜜蜂蜇  他都站着不动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Birds shat on his head, bees stung him, but he didn't budge.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.32,1:26:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在90个夜晚以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}After 90 nights …
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.21,1:26:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经变得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}he had become …
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.63,1:26:20.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又瘦又苍白  不成人样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}all dry and pale.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.80,1:26:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家无法抑制地流下了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tears streamed from his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.68,1:26:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感动的泪水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He couldn't hold them back.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.85,1:26:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵由于缺觉已经没有力气了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He didn't even have the strength to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:32.39,1:26:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而公主一直看着他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And all that time, the princess watched him.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.15,1:26:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到第99个夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When the 99th night came
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.32,1:26:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士兵站了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the soldier stood up,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.49,1:26:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放好了凳子  走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}took his chair, and left.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.83,1:26:54.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是结局啊  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Right at the end, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.41,1:26:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要问我这个故事的意义  我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't ask me what it means, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.84,1:27:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你明白了  记得告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you can figure it out, you tell me.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.92,1:27:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}好吧
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.82,1:28:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你  不要问我为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please, don't ask me why.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.80,1:28:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-艾佛特  有什么事吗  -阿德尔福神父  我要施行圣事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What is it, Alfredo? Not now, I must administer the sacrament.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.39,1:28:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-阿德尔福神父  -什么  我急需您的帮助  因为...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Father Adelfio, I need you urgently.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.26,1:28:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-因为我有个疑惑  -什么疑惑  -一个让我灵魂振动的巨大疑惑  -灵魂吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I have terrible doubts tormenting my soul.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.24,1:28:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-神父  我有罪  -这个我们之后再说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Father, I have sinned. - Do that later.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.61,1:28:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你是谁  -停下  拜托你别走  你就不能保持沉默吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please, don't turn around.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.82,1:28:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就当什么事都没发生  -我是萨尔瓦托  -可你在这里做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Just act normal. It's Salvatore. - How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.83,1:29:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佛特  你跟我说的太可怕了  我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- That's a terrible thing to say. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.01,1:29:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-面包和鱼的奇迹吗  -我总是想到它  -但这怎么可能呢  -怎么可能呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've often wondered. How is it possible?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.10,1:29:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界末日来了  我妈妈和我爸爸说的  但这是怎么流传出来的呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's terrible. Mum told Dad. How could you mistake her voice?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.60,1:29:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我  艾琳娜  我就是个傻瓜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sorry, Elena, I was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.36,1:29:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想谈谈你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I had to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.87,1:29:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳娜  你太美了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're beautiful, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.04,1:29:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就想和你说这个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's what I wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.21,1:29:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次我遇见你都无法说出完整的句子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can never find the words when I see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.42,1:29:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的美惊呆了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I get the shivers.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.88,1:29:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之  我对此无能为力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't know how other people do it.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.76,1:29:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我爱上你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I'm in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:59.68,1:30:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,神父  我有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Father, I have sinned.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.48,1:30:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以圣父圣子圣灵的名义赦免你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I absolve you from your sins
Dialogue: 0,1:30:03.73,1:30:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保持平静吧  修女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}in the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.90,1:30:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你笑起来就更美了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're even prettier when you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.58,1:30:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨尔瓦托  你对我非常绅士  你对我也很友好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're very sweet, and I like you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.63,1:30:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I'm not in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.72,1:30:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在意  我会等  -什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- It's OK. I'll wait. - For what?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.47,1:30:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-等到你也爱上我  好好听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}For you to love me. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.18,1:30:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的夜晚  我工作结束以后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Every night, after work
