Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.85,1:39:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}影片在皇家剧院继续播出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Outdoor cinema tonight at the Imperia.
