Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.53,1:43:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个讨厌的夏天什么时候才能结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When will this bloody summer end?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.20,1:43:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影里早就结束了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In a film, it'd already be over.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:34.70,1:43:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡出  切到暴风雨  不是很好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Cut, and there's a storm. Great!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:39.95,1:43:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}吓
Dialogue: 0,1:43:45.52,1:43:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}下雨了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:53.14,1:43:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他们我是乌利塞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tell them I'm Ulysses!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.96,1:43:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}乌利塞
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.65,1:44:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳娜  你什么时候...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Elena! But when …?
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.95,1:44:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天回来的  你想象不到我找了什么借口才来到这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Today. You can't imagine the excuses I made up.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.65,1:44:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索菲娅·罗兰还是那样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sophia Loren is always Sophia Loren.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.91,1:44:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修长的腿  丰满的胸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Long legs and great boobs.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.37,1:44:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像拉娜·特纳。-更漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- Like Lana Turner. - More beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.93,1:44:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}-奇奥先生  -什么
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.10,1:45:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是的多多的  交给他  这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- For Toto. You give it to him. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.54,1:45:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犹大之血  怎么办  怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The devil take me! What will I do now?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.14,1:45:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What did they say?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.10,1:45:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为战争遗孤  我本来不用服军役\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That as a war orphan, I'm exempt from military service.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:19.23,1:45:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他们可能弄错了  没办法了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But nothing doing — clerical error.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.52,1:45:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我星期五早上要去罗马  他们说10就会让我退役  过来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Must go to Rome on Friday. They say I'll be discharged in ten days.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:28.28,1:45:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨尔瓦托  你最好离开  我爸爸来了  这样最好  我们可以谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- You should go. My father's here. - Good, I'll talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.57,1:45:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这次一定会说服他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This time I'll convince him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.41,1:45:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会被说服的  他有其他安排\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, Salvatore. He has other plans for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.75,1:45:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.21,1:45:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他同事的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The son of a colleague of his.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:45.46,1:45:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样  我们之后再谈  星期四在天堂电影院等我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'll talk about it on Thursday. Wait for me at the Paradiso.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.84,1:45:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坐5路车来  我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'll get the 5 o'clock bus. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.09,1:46:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多  这是个好电影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's a good film, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:34.93,1:46:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我不懂  放一天就够了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But people here don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:37.68,1:46:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚拜托直接放明天的影片吧  这样新人好接手  好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Tonight, load tomorrow's reels, ready for the new man.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.23,1:46:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开心点  我等你  别担心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hey, cheer up! I'll wait for you, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.61,1:46:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,工作还是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No one's taking your job.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.61,1:46:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会等你  知道吗  不要这样  开心点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It'll be waiting for you. Don't look so gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.83,1:47:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}我也不知道这对你是好消息还是坏消息
Dialogue: 0,1:47:46.43,1:47:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}什么消息
Dialogue: 0,1:47:49.25,1:47:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}您丈夫过世了...
Dialogue: 0,1:47:59.39,1:48:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会是在等我吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You were expecting someone else?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:02.39,1:48:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有  我是来帮你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, Alfredo. I came down to help you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:05.64,1:48:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  是在等她吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, you were waiting for her.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:09.23,1:48:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人等多无聊  两个人好点吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Not nice waiting alone. I'll keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:15.19,1:48:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是你希望我离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe you'd rather I went.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:17.20,1:48:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别走  我需要你的帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, don't go. In fact, I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.18,1:48:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只听声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can't hear this.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.55,1:49:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门  艾琳娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Open up!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.65,1:49:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开门  艾琳娜  艾琳娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Open up! Elena!
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.26,1:49:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}奥尔多
Dialogue: 0,1:49:50.79,1:49:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\b1}剧终\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}THE END
Dialogue: 0,1:49:55.45,1:49:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}烂片
Dialogue: 0,1:50:00.59,1:50:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢  我喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I like it!
Dialogue: 0,1:50:07.23,1:50:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}多多
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.65,1:50:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:25.03,1:50:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前去哪了  不要害怕  我在  你去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Where were you? Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:29.45,1:50:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静  坐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Calm down. Here, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:37.67,1:50:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-她来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Did she come?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:40.17,1:50:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没人来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No one came.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:02.78,1:51:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三营第九连  通讯兵迪·维塔·萨尔瓦托报道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Salvatore di Vita reporting for duty.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:13.29,1:51:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校  我的退伍令下来了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I wish to know when I'll be discharged, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:15.96,1:51:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没有接到通知  便步走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No news as yet. Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:26.43,1:51:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她父亲搬家了吗  怎么可能  没人知道她家搬去哪了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Her father's been transferred and no one knows where to?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:31.60,1:51:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋  你根本不想帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sod you, bastard! You won't bloody well tell me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:44.74,1:51:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\b1}这个地址不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}NOT KNOWN AT THIS ADDRESS
Dialogue: 0,1:51:57.42,1:52:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上校我本来只用服10天役的  已经一年了  我没回过一次家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I should have done ten days and it's been a year, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:02.04,1:52:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少给我放个假吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Without a day's leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:28.95,1:52:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迪·维塔  你的退伍令已经下来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Di Vita, you've been discharged.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:44.67,1:53:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}过来
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.30,1:54:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你瘦了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've lost weight.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.97,1:54:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过得不好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They didn't treat you very well, did they?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.39,1:54:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说你从不出门  也不和人讲话  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They say you never go out or talk to anyone. Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:23.35,1:54:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.52,1:54:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,迟早会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Sooner or later, the time comes
Dialogue: 0,1:54:29.53,1:54:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管你说不说  都是一样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when it makes no difference whether you talk or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.57,1:54:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你最好闭嘴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So you might as well shut up.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:46.04,1:54:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里好热\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:49.38,1:54:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多  带我去海边吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Take me to the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:51.09,1:54:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞节的时时候  一个中尉掐了一个女孩的屁股\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}At Christmas, this lieutenant pinches a girl's bum.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.88,1:54:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩是上校的女儿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She turns round. It's the colonel's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:58.72,1:55:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,中尉惊恐地说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Terrified, he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:00.43,1:55:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你的心像你的屁股一样硬  那我就死定了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"If your heart is as hard as what I've just felt, I'm a dead man."
Dialogue: 0,1:55:11.78,1:55:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你后来见过她吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Have you seen her?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:15.52,1:55:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}没有
Dialogue: 0,1:55:17.32,1:55:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道她在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No one knows where she is.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:21.41,1:55:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或许是注定的吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It was probably meant to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.66,1:55:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都在追寻一颗星星\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Each of us has a star to follow.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.25,1:55:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在想做什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And now … what are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:44.56,1:55:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Listen to this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.98,1:55:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次长官对军士说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The commander says to the sergeant,
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.65,1:55:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得那边以前有个风车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Remember when there was a windmill there?"
Dialogue: 0,1:55:55.19,1:55:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官  我记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"Yes, sir. I remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:58.36,1:56:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在风车没有了  但是风永远都在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"The windmill's gone, but the wind's still there."
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.92,1:56:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你记得那个士兵和公主的故事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Remember the story about the soldier and the princess?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.48,1:56:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我明白士兵最后为什么离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now I understand why the soldier left right at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.36,1:56:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  只要再坚持一晚公主就是他的了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}One more night and the princess would have been his.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:40.11,1:56:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果公主没有遵守诺言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But she might not have kept her promise.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:43.78,1:56:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就太糟了  他会痛苦死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That would have been too cruel. It would have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.71,1:56:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少在那99晚里  他都觉得她在等他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This way, at least, for 99 nights he lived in hope that she'd be his.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:56.96,1:57:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像士兵一样  离开吧  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Do as the soldier, Toto. Go away from here.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:01.84,1:57:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是不幸之地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This land is cursed.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:04.89,1:57:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每天生活在这儿  会觉得自己是世界的中心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Living here every day, you think it's the centre of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:11.19,1:57:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会觉得什么都不会变\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That nothing will ever change.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:15.07,1:57:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后离开  一年  两年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then you leave, for a year or two.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:19.19,1:57:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来的时候什么都变了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And when you return everything's changed.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:21.53,1:57:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,线断了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The thread is broken.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:24.53,1:57:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找不回你想找寻的  你想要的都不在这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You don't find what you were looking for. What was yours is gone.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:30.21,1:57:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要离开很久  很多年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You need to go away for a long time, for many years
Dialogue: 0,1:57:35.42,1:57:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再来找寻你的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}before you can come back and find your people …
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.72,1:57:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你出生的土地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}the land where you were born.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:44.30,1:57:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在不可能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But not now. It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:47.22,1:57:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在比我还瞎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now you're blinder than I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:49.56,1:57:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁说的  贾利·库珀  詹姆斯·史都华  还是亨利·方达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who said that? Gary Cooper? James Stewart? Henry Fonda?
Dialogue: 0,1:57:54.31,1:57:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:57.98,1:58:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是台词\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No one said it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:01.86,1:58:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我想说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}This time, I'm saying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:05.24,1:58:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活不是电影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Life is not what you see in films.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:09.33,1:58:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活更艰难\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Life is much harder.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:15.17,1:58:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go away!
Dialogue: 0,1:58:17.25,1:58:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回罗马去  你还年轻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Go back to Rome. You're young.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:20.76,1:58:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界都是你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The world's your oyster.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:23.93,1:58:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我老了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm old.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:26.85,1:58:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再听你讲话了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't want to hear you any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:58:29.97,1:58:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想听别人谈论你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I want to hear about you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:04.86,2:00:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't come back.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:07.95,2:00:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要想我们  不要回头  不要写信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't think about us. Don't look back, don't write.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.08,2:00:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要妥协  忘了我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't give in to nostalgia. Forget about us.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.71,2:00:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你坚持不下去要回来  不要来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you come back, don't come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:22.21,2:00:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你踏进家门  懂了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I won't let you in, you understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:00:32.97,2:00:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you …
Dialogue: 0,2:00:35.72,2:00:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你为我做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}for everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:40.65,2:00:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什么工作  都要热爱它\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Whatever you end up doing, love it.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:45.57,2:00:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你爱影院的放映机一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The way you loved the projection booth
Dialogue: 0,2:00:49.53,2:00:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时你真淘气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}when you were a little boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:00.46,2:01:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经出发了吗  多多  永别了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Is he already gone? Toto, farewell!
Dialogue: 0,2:01:04.93,2:01:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}永别了
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.09,2:01:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}多多
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.34,2:01:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来晚了  好遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm too late, what a pity!
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.53,2:02:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是多多  我知道是他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's Toto. I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:33.24,2:02:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}-多多  -你还好吗  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.23,2:02:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妹妹会很高兴的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your sister Lia will be so happy to see you. And the children.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:53.36,2:02:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子们都不认识你了  他们长大了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You won't recognise them.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:56.70,2:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们总是写信告诉我想来罗马\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When are they coming to Rome?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:58.87,2:03:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道现在家里有多漂亮吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}See how nice the house is?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:01.70,2:03:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们整修过  多亏了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We've had it all redone, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:05.50,2:03:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来  我有个惊喜给你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come, I've a surprise for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:11.00,2:03:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你累了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,2:03:13.42,2:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要休息吗  葬礼之前都可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You've time to rest before the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:16.47,2:03:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不了  妈妈  一个小时后的飞机\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No, Mum. The flight is only an hour.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:20.39,2:03:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年了  不能说走就走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't say that, after all these years.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:24.18,2:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来  我把所有东西都放这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Come, I've put all your things in here.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.71,2:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你来了他会很高兴的  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He must be glad you came, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:20.72,2:05:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他总是谈起你  总是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He always talked about you, always.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.31,2:05:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后一刻  他想你...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Right up to the end.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.23,2:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很想你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He really loved you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:49.16,2:05:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他给你留了两样东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He left something for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.87,2:05:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Before you leave
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.25,2:05:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来找我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}come and see me.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:57.32,2:06:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}-谁啊  -是他  是他
Dialogue: 0,2:07:31.18,2:07:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}早安
Dialogue: 0,2:07:42.48,2:07:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关门多久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When did you close it down?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:45.40,2:07:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到五月就六年了  没有人来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Six years ago in May. No one ever came.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:49.95,2:07:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您比我更清楚  经济危机  电视  磁带...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know it better than I do. The recession, TV, videos …
Dialogue: 0,2:07:55.75,2:07:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影只存在于梦里了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The cinema has become a memory.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.17,2:08:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在政府买下它作为停车场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The city has purchased the site for a public car park.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.51,2:08:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期六就要拆掉了  真遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're pulling down on Saturday, Signor di Vita. Pity!
Dialogue: 0,2:08:10.39,2:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么称我为"您"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why "Signor di Vita?"
Dialogue: 0,2:08:13.56,2:08:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前不是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It didn't use to be like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:15.60,2:08:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,称一个重要人物为"你"太困难了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's awkward to be casual with an important person.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.48,2:08:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果你坚持  我还是叫你多多吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}However, if you insist … Toto.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.20,2:08:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失陪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.08,2:08:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁能想到呢  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who would have believed it? Toto.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:09.90,2:09:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅  下次外婆去罗马的时候  我也想去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Uncle, next time grandma goes to Rome, I'll go with her.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:13.74,2:09:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看你在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I want to see where you work.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:16.29,2:09:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  但其实没什么好看的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}OK, but there's not much to see.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.41,2:09:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是雷声大雨点小\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My job is much ado about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:24.25,2:09:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可别上当\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Careful, Salvatore.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:28.01,2:09:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们俩比食人者还坏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're worse than cannibals, they'll take advantage of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:33.93,2:09:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舅舅  你明天出发吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Are you off tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,2:09:39.56,2:09:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  我真的不知道，菲利波\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I don't know. I really don't know, Filippo.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.67,2:10:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是找你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Must be for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.71,2:10:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整个下午都在打电话  他们想知道你今晚还是明天出发\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They've been ringing all day asking when you'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:30.67,2:13:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两杯威士忌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Double whisky, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:37.38,2:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}对对  是他
Dialogue: 0,2:13:43.01,2:13:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问你是洛林先生吗  我是你的粉丝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Excuse me, aren't you Dr Lénera? I'm a fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:53.86,2:13:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.08,2:15:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}小姐
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.52,2:15:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,2:15:10.47,2:15:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我认错人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm so sorry, I thought you were someone else.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:33.52,2:16:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}总是我给你打电话
Dialogue: 0,2:16:35.85,2:16:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是现在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's always me ringing.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:37.77,2:16:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你中午来接我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I asked you to pick me up at lunchtime.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:41.73,2:16:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Forget it, I'm not going.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.78,2:16:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用管我了  我自己走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In fact, I'll go on my own.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.08,2:17:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多多  你在想什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What are you thinking, Toto?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:40.79,2:17:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想...  我们从没有聊过天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We've never really talked, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:48.46,2:17:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候我觉得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I was little, I saw you …
Dialogue: 0,2:17:53.47,2:17:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你已经老了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}as an old woman already.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:56.85,2:17:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能所有子女都会这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Maybe all kids are like that, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:09.24,2:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在我才发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's taken me all this time …
Dialogue: 0,2:18:13.28,2:18:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时你很年轻  很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to realise that you were young then, and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:19.12,2:18:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有美好的人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You had your whole life ahead of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:23.37,2:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你为什么总是一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why, then? Why did you stay on your own?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:28.84,2:18:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有和别人在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Without anyone to look after you.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:32.80,2:18:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你本可以再婚的  为什么没有呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You could have remarried. Why didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:39.89,2:18:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我不懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I might not have understood at the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.02,2:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But later … yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:48.27,2:18:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有和任何人在一起过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There was never anyone, if that's what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.32,2:18:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.57,2:18:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是很忠贞  对你父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I remained faithful, first to your father
Dialogue: 0,2:18:57.87,2:19:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你  对丽娅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and then to you and Lia.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:01.08,2:19:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只能做到这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's the way I am, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:19:04.87,2:19:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很像我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And you're like me.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:08.00,2:19:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你热爱的事物很忠诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're too attached to the past.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.51,2:19:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道这是否是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm not sure it's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:15.01,2:19:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忠诚是一个很可怕的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Being faithful has its drawbacks.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.14,2:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你忠诚  你就会永远一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Fidelity brings loneliness.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:29.69,2:19:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不该给你打电话的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I shouldn't have called you.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:33.74,2:19:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别管他们了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's not your fault, Mum.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:36.16,2:19:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是害怕回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've always been afraid to come back.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:42.16,2:19:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Now, after all these years …
Dialogue: 0,2:19:45.71,2:19:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我会更坚强  会忘记很多事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I thought I was stronger and had forgotten many things.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:52.17,2:19:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是  所有事都浮现在眼前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But it's all right there in front of me …
Dialogue: 0,2:19:58.14,2:20:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎我从未离开\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}as if I'd never gone away.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:02.43,2:20:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我看着丽娅就好像是陌生人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And yet, I hardly know Lia.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:09.36,2:20:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有你  妈妈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And you, Mum …
Dialogue: 0,2:20:12.57,2:20:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我抛弃了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I deserted you.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:15.78,2:20:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我像强盗一样逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I ran away like a criminal.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:17.95,2:20:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从未给你解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Without an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:19.95,2:20:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不需要解释  你不需要解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I never asked for one. You don't have to explain.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:24.25,2:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你做的是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I always thought you were doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:27.92,2:20:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用去追究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't dwell on it.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:30.33,2:20:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一件事让我痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Only one thing bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:32.96,2:20:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚睡觉前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}At night, before I went to bed,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.76,2:20:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关门的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.93,2:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以前不关门的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- You never used to. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:44.77,2:20:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  你以前晚上在电影院工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When you worked in the cinema, late at night,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:48.44,2:20:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不回家  我都睡不着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I could never sleep till you got home.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:54.90,2:20:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当你回到家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then, when you got back,
Dialogue: 0,2:20:58.03,2:21:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就假装睡着了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I pretended to be asleep.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:00.91,2:21:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我能感觉到你的所有动作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I was aware of all your movements.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:03.58,2:21:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我就起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Then, when you were asleep, I'd get up
Dialogue: 0,2:21:08.21,2:21:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关门\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and lock the door.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:12.75,2:21:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后来你离开了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}After you'd gone …
Dialogue: 0,2:21:17.26,2:21:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我每次去关门的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}whenever I did that
Dialogue: 0,2:21:19.93,2:21:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都觉得把谁远远地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I felt as though I was locking someone out.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:24.76,2:21:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关在了门外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Shutting him off.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:27.85,2:21:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你离开是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You were right to leave.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:30.31,2:21:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你实现了自己的梦想\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It allowed you to do what you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:35.27,2:21:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次我给你打电话  都是不同的女人接的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When I phone you, it's a different woman every time.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:39.86,2:21:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我装作认识她们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I pretend that I know them
Dialogue: 0,2:21:42.62,2:21:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不让她们尴尬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}to avoid embarrassing introductions.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:47.16,2:21:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯定她们觉得我是疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I bet they take me for a dotty old woman.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.67,2:21:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我至今没有听到  真正爱你的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I haven't yet heard the voice of someone who really loves you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.63,2:22:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I can tell, you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:02.64,2:22:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很想看到你安定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}All the same, I'd like to see you settling down.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:08.64,2:22:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和别人相爱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}In love with someone.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:11.94,2:22:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你的生活在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But your life is there.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:14.44,2:22:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有鬼魂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Here, there are only ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:17.44,2:22:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧  多多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Let go, Toto.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:23.09,2:23:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Boccia!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:31.77,2:23:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫罗·梅奥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}His name was Lo Meo.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.82,2:23:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}温琴佐
Dialogue: 0,2:23:44.04,2:23:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}喂
Dialogue: 0,2:23:46.80,2:23:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}喂
Dialogue: 0,2:23:49.44,2:23:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}喂
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.49,2:24:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂  谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hello! Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:39.17,2:24:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找艾琳娜女士  我就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}- May I speak to Signora Elena? - Speaking.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:44.46,2:24:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:48.22,2:24:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨尔瓦托  萨尔瓦托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Salvatore.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:57.06,2:24:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:00.23,2:25:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是萨尔瓦托·迪维塔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Di Vita. I'm Salvatore di Vita.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:06.53,2:25:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Remember me?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:09.20,2:25:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在你家楼下的酒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm ringing from the bar across the road, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:26.42,2:25:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Of course I remember you.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:32.59,2:25:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想见你  艾琳娜  我们见面吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd like to see you, Elena. Let's meet.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.43,2:25:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经过去很久了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:41.10,2:25:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要见面呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why should we meet?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:44.40,2:25:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么用呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What good would it do?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:47.11,2:25:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  不要拒绝我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Please, don't say no.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:50.11,2:25:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨尔瓦托  我老了  你也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'm old, Salvatore. And so are you.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:54.24,2:25:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不见面比较好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's best not to see each other.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:57.89,2:25:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}再见
Dialogue: 0,2:26:28.79,2:26:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}喂
Dialogue: 0,2:27:35.32,2:27:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\b0\bord0\shad0}萨尔瓦托
Dialogue: 0,2:28:07.83,2:28:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How did you know I'd be here?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:11.46,2:28:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道过去多少年了  但是你的事我都记得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's been a long time, but I haven't forgotten certain things.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:16.59,2:28:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有多少地方可去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}There aren't many places you'd go to.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:22.31,2:28:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I did the rounds.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:42.91,2:28:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还是那么美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You're still beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.71,2:28:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢  我老了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What are you saying? I'm old.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.34,2:28:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样看着我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Don't look at me like that.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:03.43,2:29:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Why have you come back?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:07.14,2:29:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佛特去世了  你记得他吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Alfredo's dead. Remember him?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:12.77,2:29:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然记得  很遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Of course I remember him. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:20.07,2:29:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很爱他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You were very fond of him.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:24.79,2:29:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你的女儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I saw your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:27.75,2:29:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}She's very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:32.00,2:29:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道有多少个萨尔瓦托在追她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}God knows how many Salvatores she's got in tow.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:36.46,2:29:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人追\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A few.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:39.55,2:29:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是叫萨尔瓦托的应该不多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But there are not many Salvatores.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:46.39,2:29:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还有个大儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I've a son, too. He's older.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:52.48,2:29:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And you?
Dialogue: 0,2:29:53.65,2:29:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有子女  也没有结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No children. I never married.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:01.20,2:30:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你幸福吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You happy?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:03.03,2:30:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总的来看很幸福\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I am, all things considered.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:07.24,2:30:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和我那时的梦想不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Though it's not what I dreamt of.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:13.33,2:30:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识我丈夫吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You know my husband, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:18.67,2:30:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么不认识  博加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Boccia, I remember him well.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:23.34,2:30:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他做什么工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What does he do? What's his job?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:28.35,2:30:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政治  他是区议员\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He's a politician. A local councillor.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:35.48,2:30:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在比萨大学重逢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We met again at Pisa University.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:41.24,2:30:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么没和你父亲同事的儿子结婚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How come you didn't marry your father's …?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:44.53,2:30:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想  最后我赢了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't want to. I got my own way in the end.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:54.08,2:30:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后...我在等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was still waiting for you at the time.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:02.84,2:31:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我从没有忘记你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I never forgot you. Never.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:07.35,2:31:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Neither did I.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:11.06,2:31:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Even though you'd disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:17.94,2:31:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在说这些有什么用呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But why talk about it now?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:26.16,2:31:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只是在冒着可怜又可笑的风险  -你一直住在罗马吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's pathetic, and absurd. You still live in Rome?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:31.91,2:31:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你说什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,2:31:34.62,2:31:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们最后一次见面  我们约好在天堂电影院  你记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}We'd arranged to meet at the Paradiso.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:38.09,2:31:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你没来  你什么都没说就消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But you never showed up. Not a word, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:42.96,2:31:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多少年过去了  30多年了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}How long ago was it? Over 30 years.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:50.93,2:31:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I …
Dialogue: 0,2:31:52.97,2:31:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去了那个约会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I did show up.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:03.94,2:32:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我去晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I was late.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:08.03,2:32:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和我父母吵架了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I'd quarrelled with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:13.12,2:32:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试着说服他们不要拆散我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Trying to convince them not to come between us.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:18.96,2:32:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有用\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But it was no use.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:23.46,2:32:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们决定永远离开西西里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They'd made up their minds to leave Sicily once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:31.85,2:32:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后这变成了事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And that's what we did.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:35.31,2:32:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该做什么  说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't know what do, what to say.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:41.31,2:32:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我同意了  做了他们想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So I agreed to do what they wanted.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:48.91,2:32:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换我爸爸同意我见你最后一面  和你告别\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I convinced my father to let me see you one last time.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:56.16,2:32:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算只要见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was hoping …
Dialogue: 0,2:32:59.17,2:33:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就可以一起做决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}we'd take a decision when we met.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:05.92,2:33:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为也许…\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I thought maybe …
Dialogue: 0,2:33:09.84,2:33:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以私奔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}we'd run away together.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:18.23,2:33:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸陪我去了电影院  但是你不在放映室  只有艾佛特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My father took me to the cinema. But Alfredo was there, not you.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:26.74,2:33:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有时间等你回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I couldn't wait for you to come back.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:32.95,2:33:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾琳娜  快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Hurry up, Elena.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:34.58,2:33:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉艾佛特所发生的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I told Alfredo what was happening.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:37.91,2:33:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他我当晚就离开  我求他帮我转达\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I said we were going away and asked him to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:45.71,2:33:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他人很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He was very nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:48.67,2:33:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很认真听我讲话  然后...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He listened to me patiently.
Dialogue: 0,2:33:54.60,2:33:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  别这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Calm down, don't get upset.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:00.19,2:34:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Listen to what I have to say.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:02.90,2:34:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想让我向多多转达你说的话  我可以帮你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you want me to tell Toto, I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:08.03,2:34:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果你想听我的建议  还是算了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But if you want my advice, let it be.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:12.70,2:34:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不见面对你俩都好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}It's best for you two to stay apart.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:16.66,2:34:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲爱的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}My dear child …
Dialogue: 0,2:34:20.33,2:34:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,火总会燃成灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Out of the fire of love come ashes.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:23.25,2:34:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱也会逝去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Even the greatest love eventually fizzles out.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:27.13,2:34:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以后会有更多其他的爱情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You'll meet other people, plenty of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:31.68,2:34:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是多多只有一个未来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But there's only one future for Toto.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:35.10,2:34:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是他现在不懂  也不会相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He doesn't know it yet, and wouldn't believe me if I told him.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:39.64,2:34:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至会想杀了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He'd kill me if I did.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:43.81,2:34:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你能懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But you, my dear … you can understand.
Dialogue: 0,2:34:48.11,2:34:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须懂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You must understand. Do it for him.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:10.51,2:35:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个秘密我本来不想告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I never wanted anyone to know my secret, not even you.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:21.98,2:35:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的艾佛特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Bloody Alfredo!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:26.60,2:35:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也迷惑了你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He charmed everyone, even you.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:31.07,2:35:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听从了他的建议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I said I'd follow his advice.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:33.82,2:35:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是出发前  我给你留了纸条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I left a note for you before I left.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:48.34,2:35:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我下楼梯时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was on my way down.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:52.34,2:35:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到艾佛特看不见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I knew Alfredo couldn't see me.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:57.43,2:35:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}So I went back up.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:01.81,2:36:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他坐在放映机前一动不动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I saw him sitting there, by the projector.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:07.48,2:36:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我取下一张墙上的纸条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I took one of those bits of paper on the wall.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:12.40,2:36:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你写了我的地址\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And wrote a note saying where to find me.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:17.53,2:36:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及我会等你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And that I'd wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:23.95,2:36:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你还是消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But you disappeared all the same.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:37.13,2:36:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找了你很多次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you knew how I searched for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:42.47,2:36:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}You can't imagine.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:45.89,2:36:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我写过信  打过电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I wrote, I phoned … nothing.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:50.77,2:36:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来没有人回应\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No one ever replied.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:57.15,2:36:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我逃走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's why I left …
Dialogue: 0,2:37:03.24,2:37:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}and never came back.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:08.12,2:37:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直梦见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But for years I dreamt of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:22.35,2:37:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管时间流逝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Time went by.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:25.52,2:37:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在遇见的所有女人中  我只想找到你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Yet I looked for you in every woman I ever met.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:32.65,2:37:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的事业很成功  的确很成功\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I was lucky in my career. Very lucky, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:40.95,2:37:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我总是缺少什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:46.74,2:37:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有想到  造成这一切的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I could never have imagined it would be the fault
Dialogue: 0,2:37:53.13,2:37:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那个我视为父亲的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}of the man who was like a father to me.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:57.59,2:37:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,疯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}A mad man!
Dialogue: 0,2:38:00.05,2:38:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是疯子  刚开始我也恨他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He wasn't mad. I hated him at first.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:04.55,2:38:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是后来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But as time went by …
Dialogue: 0,2:38:07.85,2:38:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了他的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I understood his advice.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:11.94,2:38:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和你的沉默\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I understood your silence.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:15.98,2:38:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我从未见过那张纸条\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But I never found that note.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:20.78,2:38:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己盖住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I covered it with my own hands.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:24.95,2:38:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有发现  这是唯一的解释\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}I didn't see it, there's no other explanation.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:28.70,2:38:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在找原因不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No point explaining any more.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:33.25,2:38:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经过去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}That's how it was.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:36.42,2:38:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾佛特没有背叛你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But Alfredo didn't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:38.92,2:38:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是唯一让你想清楚的办法  萨尔瓦托\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He knew you better than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:45.43,2:38:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你选择了我  就不会拍电影\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}If you'd chosen to stay with me, you'd never have made any films.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:48.26,2:38:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会有多遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And that would have been a great pity.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:50.48,2:38:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是好电影  我都看过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}They're such beautiful films. I've seen them all.
Dialogue: 0,2:38:57.65,2:39:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不该改名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}But you shouldn't have changed your name.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:01.90,2:39:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该叫萨尔瓦托·迪维塔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}What's wrong with your name?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:19.06,2:40:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是他留给你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He left this for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:36.71,2:40:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每当电视里播你的电影  他都很开心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}When they showed your films on television, he was happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:45.38,2:40:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他总是坐在那里  度过一切疾病\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He just sat in front of the TV and forgot all his ailments.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:52.72,2:40:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他记得台词每一句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He knew every single word by heart.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:56.43,2:41:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我给他解说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And I told him what the images were.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:00.31,2:41:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当报纸谈论你  我要给他读两三遍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}And when you were in the papers, he'd make me read it again and again.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:10.66,2:41:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他从没想过见我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He never asked to see me?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:12.37,2:41:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}No. Never.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:16.87,2:41:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一次你妈妈告诉我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Your mother once said
Dialogue: 0,2:41:19.83,2:41:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他想  你一定会来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}you'd come if he wanted you to.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:24.75,2:41:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他发火\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He was furious. He said,
Dialogue: 0,2:41:27.55,2:41:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说  不行  多多绝不能回来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}"No. Toto must never return to Giancaldo."
Dialogue: 0,2:41:34.93,2:41:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有恶意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He wasn't being mean.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:37.64,2:41:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一个虔诚的基督教徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:40.81,2:41:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道他在想什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Who knows what went through his head?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:44.98,2:41:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后关头也在说一些胡话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}He started saying strange things towards the end.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:51.82,2:41:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭眼之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Just before he closed his eyes …
Dialogue: 0,2:41:55.87,2:41:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他让你母亲不要通知你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}he told your mother not to let you know.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:13.97,2:42:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,77  76  68  不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}1977, 1976, 1968 …
Dialogue: 0,2:42:43.33,2:42:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《白鲸记》[赫尔曼·梅尔维尔小说]\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Moby Dick.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:47.80,2:42:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《抽屉里的梦》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Dreams in a Drawer.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:50.76,2:42:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《挑战》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Challenge.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.26,2:42:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《野生之道》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}The Searchers.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:59.02,2:43:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《妄执》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Magnificent Obsession.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:03.44,2:43:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,《呐喊》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs12}{\b0}{\c&HFFFFFF&}{\3c&H2F2F2F&}{\4c&H000000&}Il Grido.
